Current idea for how games will probably be saved

FILE Settings
FOLDER [Game Name] (1 for each game)
  FILE Game Parameters
  FILE Tokens
  FILE Tiles
  FOLDER Maps
    FILE [Map Name] (1 for each map)
  FOLDER Images
    FOLDER Tokens
      IMG files
    FOLDER Tiles
      IMG files
    
Settings
  User settings such as what game was open last and how the program should look
Game Parameters
  Holds data for the game as a whole, such as what is the current map that should be displayed
